2688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15c985427fcd7f0e56ebd853c249ed81f08df493","tid":1352080,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:07:15.000Z","msg":"覺得自己咩都做唔到？仲有一樣野你實做到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351987\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351987</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d9aecee16d9cc467aa7a131a3320bc55aa8f73a","tid":1352080,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T18:08:50.000Z","msg":"就每個post都留上環post link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醒呀連登仔！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(超級Backup台)(721)上環+元朗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1351576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1351576</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［721上環影片/圖片集結post]屌你上環都好撚重要！！！文宣組入黎幫手推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349459\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349459</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！</span><br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"ebc34196e5c8ff623e1dae02f801ce58015edc72","tid":1352080,"uid":274513,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"873481aa0414cbd76b196d26211434836b23f35b","tid":1352080,"uid":141793,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"cit